KitKat2::
She smiled and put her hand on Starscream's shoulder. "It's great to 
see you again. I'm glad your doing well. I missed you guys, all of 
you."  She smiled and moved back so he could follow Drillbit. She 
went to the station and looked at DarkMouse. "Will you always be 
making public service anouncements?"

DarkMouse::
She smirked. "Hey, I always wanted a warm reception when I got back 
from missions, not an electric shock in the back."  She turned and 
went back to her duties. "Besides, it get's boring sitting here. I'd 
like to go ut and have fun once in a while too you know."

KitKat2::
She nodded. "I understand. Why not ask Drillbit for your turn to go 
out and fight?"

DarkMouse::
"Because I'm the best at computer systems out of this whole bunch, 
that's why."

KitKat2:: 
"Got a point there. Oh well, think about it anyway." She turned and 
left. She headed for the CR room.
